<span id="freeTextContainer6151475688368572646">Many fresh and flavorful dishes and food photos inspired by the idea of the summer season with equally enticing Nigella commentary. Key ingredients can be plucked from your garden or the local farm market. The recipes are honest, fun and fairly simple to put together. A few favorites: spiced pink soup, the rainbow room&apos;s carrot and peanut salad, lavender trust cupcakes, rhubarb fool, fresh green gimlet. </span>
  <span id="freeText6151475688368572646" style="display:none">Many fresh and flavorful dishes and food photos inspired by the idea of the summer season with equally enticing Nigella commentary. Key ingredients can be plucked from your garden or the local farm market. The recipes are honest, fun and fairly simple to put together. A few favorites: spiced pink soup, the rainbow room's carrot and peanut salad, lavender trust cupcakes, rhubarb fool, fresh green gimlet. </span>
