        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer29381086" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8188583803938853631">This is a great cook book. I love the penne and asparagus recipe, the pork chops are also a favorite. Plus Lawsons writing style and direction takes all of the fuss out of cooking and just makes it seem so cool and effortless. I LoVE this woman! </span>

          </span>
